                            <p style="padding: 10% 0px 3% 0px;font-size: 23px;color: black; font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif,';">In a survey for school students, when asked about “What form of Motivation you prefer?” the following results were obtained.

<br><br>Verbal encouragement 30%
<br>Tangible rewards 53%
<br>I am self-motivated 18%*
